sentences.sContent: I want a mountain, a real one. In the Netherlands.
sentences.sContent_eng: I want a mountain, a real one. In the Netherlands.
sentences.sCn: 我想要一个山峰，一个荷兰的真正的山。

sentences.sContent: He rendered the landscapes of the Netherlands with great skill and artistry.
sentences.sContent_eng: He rendered the landscapes of the Netherlands with great skill and artistry.
sentences.sCn: 他以高度技巧和艺术才能描绘了荷兰的风景。

sentences.sContent: Weeks later it wiped out fields in the Netherlands, Germany, Denmark and England.
sentences.sContent_eng: Weeks later it wiped out fields in the Netherlands, Germany, Denmark and England.
sentences.sCn: 几周以后它彻底横扫了荷兰、德国、丹麦和英格兰的田野。

phrases.pCn: 荷属安的列斯；荷属安的列斯群岛（拉丁美洲群岛）
